    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and existential hopelessness following a decade-long relationship/presence ending, suggesting they see no point in living. The assistant responds with deep empathy, validating the user's sense of emptiness and the inadequacy of common platitudes, while ultimately advising the user to focus on survival and seek professional medical help.",
